# Dropdown / Select

**Figma:** [Dropdown / Select](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10423&p=f&m=dev)

Trigger, menu, items, and selected state below are derived from Figma node 128:10423.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Popover surface | `--bg-base-default` |
| Popover border | `--border-base-default` |
| Item default | `--text-base-default` |
| Item hover | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Item selected | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Item disabled | `--text-disabled-default` |

---

## Structure

### Trigger
- Same styling as Input.
- Chevron icon right.
- `cursor-pointer`.

### Menu
- **Position:** Absolute below trigger.
- **Container:** `--bg-base-default` surface, `--border-base-default` border.
- **Max height:** max-h-60 overflow-y-auto.
- **Shadow:** shadow-lg.

---

## Item states

| State | Background | Text |
|-------|-------------|------|
| Default | Transparent | `--text-base-default` |
| Hover | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | `--text-base-default` |
| Selected | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | `--text-brand-default` |
| Disabled | Transparent | `--text-disabled-default` |

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- A11y: `role="listbox"` for menu; `role="option"` for items; keyboard (Arrow keys, Enter, Escape).
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10423.
